Package: alex-tools
Section: utils
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
    ${misc:Depends}
Description: Various Command Line Tools
 This package includes various tools I like to use around my Linux machines.
 Some of the entries are just shell scripts I use for example to list rules
 in my firewall.

Package: alex-tools-gui
Section: utils
Architecture: any
Depends: vim-gtk3, alex-tools,
    ${shlibs:Depends},
    ${misc:Depends}
Description: Various Command Line Tools requiring X-Windows
 This package is used along the alex-tools package, but it includes
 dependencies and tools that require X-Windows (more specifically, Gnome).

